Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神 光與影的一族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,細心傾聽我的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我造出光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時亦造出闇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那並非你們的最終形態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們將來會變為完全形態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一天來臨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會豎立這塊石板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個世界分為光與影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由神所造的石板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知給甚麼人擊碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影的一族互相懷疑對方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展開廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中有這樣的記載
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閱讀這塊石板便會無所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 會讀這塊石板上的文字的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有光與影之間的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那個人會帶來新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 光與影的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了解開那個謎 得到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們開始尋找石板的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且戰鬥了一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一話  [ 光與影的傳說 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多麼的舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來又是這個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然夢中的風景我從未見過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總是覺得很親切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來已經這麼晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些在廣闊清澈的藍天上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕飄飄的白色的東西是甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 去問爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢…蠢才！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你有空為那種無聊的夢來問我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如去練劍吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個夢一定是光之…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達西奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾要去練劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要妨礙他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 爸爸 無論我多努力練劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不會讓我取得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟光之一族戰鬥所需的許可書…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍士的証書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下 那…那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡陛下擔心你會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為殿下你無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是影之一族重要的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 禾斯加陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那麼想得到劍士的証書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便跟你練劍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了…！我自己一個人去練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使爸爸叫我去練劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不會給我劍士的証書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見莎朗 練習已經完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲…厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾…我的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的人品非常好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔 關心別人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他是王子 完全配得起我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾斯托爾高強一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 好像凱撒一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不會那麼奢望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最低限度 只要他成為劍士…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別那樣子為難我啊 莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然偏偏是凱撒 對手太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗的胴體何時看也那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無得彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那種地方做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎…莎朗託我清除通風口的蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是卡托拿 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下！請你不要嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為何那麼匆忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點忘記了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次大件事 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之一族的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝破西面頂層的城門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次不是剛剛擊退他們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次好像是更大規模的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒大人已經率領軍隊前去迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正奉命趕去向禾斯卡陛下報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且要求派兵增援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒要求增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡托拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點是西面頂層的城門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真性感！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有劍士証書的你有何作為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 有人擁有証書亦幫不了忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下的確沒有劍士証書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是他父王陛下的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎麼也不用那樣說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是嚴厲的教訓她一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為莎朗大人早晚也是你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你現在不給她一點下馬威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將來便會抬不起頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法子 他真懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格剛烈的禾斯卡陛下的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不快點去報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大王陛下便會大發雷霆！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法布利陛下 形勢對我們有利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用我親自出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點能耐的劍士也只有那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像是影之一族的首席劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我有劍士的証書…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便不用給莎朗瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這種地方做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做甚麼…喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要劍士的証書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓禾斯卡陛下知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不能無條件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把劍士的証書交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你沒有劍士的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？他不在經常去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我已經找過很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡陛下 你為何那麼急著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找艾斯托爾殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據報告 光之一族的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來跟以往的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 依我的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很快便會發動總攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防我有甚麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想首先告訴艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說那種不吉利的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一禾斯卡陛下你有不測
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時我亦不會苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡陛下你長生不死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你那樣說！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不過是血肉之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終有一日都會死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想告訴艾斯托爾殿下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是石板 Words Worth 碎片的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我想訴艾斯托爾和你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把敵人想搶回的石板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth 的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收藏在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛…陛下你也告訴我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如待我轉告艾斯托爾殿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我會待你們一起才說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在做甚麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點去把艾斯托爾殿下找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要跟這麼厲害的對手比試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒和莎朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦曾經打倒這班傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害！艾斯托爾殿下！還差一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想在考試裡合格…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海特竟然合格…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在…難以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海特大人合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是簡單一點的考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單一點的考試？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考試不是…一視同仁的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換言之…這個考試的內容…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為艾斯托爾殿下你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備了最困難的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…妳的…好意！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 艾斯托爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！只要有了這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很厲害！艾斯托爾殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡能去到城堡的西面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但裡面又髒又窄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經習慣 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼…我自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下 請你小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽聞光之一族裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有法力高強的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祝你平安歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mistral Wind！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的女兒 很本事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有蘇雲娜 她不想輸給瑪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下你認識她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想跟她上床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗！\N你沒事吧？凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人的劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來比那個叫凱撒的男人還厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久沒鬥志高昂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！\N凱撒 你上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好機會！史塔利安！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法布利陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上撤退 重整陣形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把那個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先姦後殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！你做甚麼！？不！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久沒嚐過光族的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要享受個夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳頭是粉紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也是粉紅色嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…！停手…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到俘虜中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妳這種非劍士的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停…停手！你這個 [馬人]！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爺我有名字的！我叫史塔利安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這樣幹妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳那種反抗會令大爺我興奮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料…是粉紅色 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…！求求你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前進的速度這麼緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知需要多久才去到西面城門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該走哪個方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我更加更加興奮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原…原來是史塔利安的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要教訓妳這種狂妄的丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！若你把我的戒指還給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便任你魚肉 求求你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看來不明白自己的處境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要捏得那麼大力…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是俘虜 妳以為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳有資格跟大爺我講條件嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好痛！不要搖得那麼大力！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我！若你不還給我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳哭會令我喪失戰意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有忍耐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有妳的戒指嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不可說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那一隻！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mistral Wind！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡托拿！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史塔利安 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這種地方做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔…我好像把戒指還給那丫頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丫頭？\N是秘密…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這頭蠢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又把女俘虜帶進審問房
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嗎叫我蠢馬！你這個骷髏怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有盔甲 你不過是一頭種馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是大爺我最討厭的稱呼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,種馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個沒靈魂的空殼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最討厭那個稱呼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很柔軟…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常迷人！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛的胸脯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:22:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要捏…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉我還想救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭影之一族
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別緊張 我幫妳斬斷腳上的繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不抬起一點膝頭會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛…剛才很危險啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…我斬傷了妳這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,割傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？沒有流血
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插得那麼大力…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:23:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…把手指插進去…！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那樣對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別插進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那話兒…變得這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插進去嗎？\N不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.12,0:24:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想插進去\N不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.54,0:24:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想插進去\N不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.71,0:24:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好痛…！停手…求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.27,0:24:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這裡濕溜溜的 很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很不舒服…快拔出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是妳這種女孩子應該說的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.90,0:24:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拔出來…！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.20,0:25:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得拔了出來…別插進去…！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.17,0:25:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又插進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.06,0:25:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…這麼大力…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止…！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.78,0:25:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？那要加倍落力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.41,0:25:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.54,0:25:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒…舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳叫甚麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.46,0:25:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.22,0:25:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉亞 妳這裡夾得我這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.10,0:26:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…！求求你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.69,0:26:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…！不…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.84,0:26:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.00,0:26:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說) 第一話完  待續
